DISCLAIMER: This field guide is for informational and educational
purposes only. It is NOT a substitute for professional wildlife
identification. The Southern Pacific Rattlesnake is the only
dangerously venomous snake in LA County — if bitten, call 911
immediately. Never handle wild animals. Maintain safe distance
from all wildlife. The author assumes no liability for any injury
or harm resulting from use of this guide.

